Abstract = {Criminal activities, socially unacceptable behavior occurs in large
   enterprises (e.g., governments and global corporations) all too often
   undetected for years. In this paper we describe an easy to install and
   use web based intelligent parallel system to quickly search enterprise
   level email systems. The system is tailored for English, but we outline
   how the system can be adapted for other languages. We demonstrate the
   system's usefulness on the publically available Enron email data set.},
