   System Science, Henan Polytechn Univ, Jiaozuo, PEOPLES R CHINA, MAY
   15-17, 2008},
Abstract = {Email has met tremendous popularity over the past few years. Its widely
   use promotes the communication. At the same time, it gives facilities to
   terrorist organizations and illegal community. Security problem lurks
   around the course of communication. Internet Crime has become one
   notable characteristic of the collectivizing crime. This paper aims at
   the requirement of the massive email data processing and the practical
   demand. It discusses the following issues: firstly, we utilized
   community structure mining algorithm and the core individual searching
   algorithm to analyzed the email address network based on its sociality
   characteristic; secondly, we made use of database programming language
   to resolve the key technology problem of email classification and email
   social network analysis. All of the efforts are in order to discover the
   sensitive community structure and master their unlawful activities
   accurately and rapidly. We attempted to do something available to
   address the Network security problem, at the same time explored some new
   methods to solve massive data problem during the email processing. In
   the experiment, we made full use of efficient PL/SQL language to operate
   database straightly for the sake of filtering the content information
   and analyzing the email network structure, finally validated the
   effectiveness of our methods.},
