Abstract = {The purpose of this study was to application of artificial intelligence
   and monitoring devices on prevention of public disorder crimes and
   disorderly conduct. The article presents some urgent issues and
   scientific basis for artificial intelligence application and public
   monitoring devices in preventing public disorder crime and disorderly
   conduct at present and in the near future. the author has used a
   combination of traditional research methods of the scientific social and
   legal sciences such as the method of legal analysis, legal assessment,
   legal comparison and expert to achieve the goal of the study. Data were
   collected from official documents, books, independent reports,
   newspapers and related parties' analysis. Results shows that it is
   necessary to promote research and application of scientific and
   technological achievements, especially the application of artificial
   intelligence to building a large database system for the State
   management of crime prevention, including prevention of public disorder
   crimes and disorderly conduct, contributing to the country's
   socio-economic development towards civilization, modernity and
